ygData.messageBody:
Also ment to say, the gnolls are lvl's 7 - 21, very rarely I've seen a 20
or 21 though. Also by day the gnolls spawn, by night undead spawn, try
killing a few exhumed gnolls, they have some cool stuff.


>You can also find them in a gnoll spawn that has high shaman (they drop em)
>in Lake Rathe Tear. The camp is right in front of the South Karana zone
path.
>Happy Hunting
>
